<p>'The facade is simply divine and it really captures the interest of locals whenever they walk past,' she told realestate.com.au.</p>

<p>Ms Kennedy described the house as the perfect space for young families, with enough room for kids to play while parents and guests relax in others. </p>

<p>The house has already proved popular among prospective buyers since it hit the market with a guide price of $2.5million last week.</p>
